# 🎬 Ultra Downloader Pro

A full-stack web app that allows users to **download high-quality videos and audio** from platforms like **YouTube**, **Instagram**, and **Facebook** — including **private/restricted** content using cookie-based authentication.

> ⚡ Powered by Flask & yt-dlp • Secure 🔒 • Modern UI • Deployable on Render

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

- 🚀 *Coming soon on [Render](https://render.com)*  
- 🛠️ Deploy it yourself via: [Render Deploy Config](https://render.com)

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Supports downloads from **YouTube**, **Instagram**, and **Facebook**
- 🔐 **Cookie-based login** for private or restricted content
- 🎵 Download in **MP4 / MP3** – Best available quality
- ⚡ **Multithreaded** download support for faster processing
- 🧹 Auto-delete server file after browser download
- 🖤 Clean and modern **Dark UI** for better UX

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer     | Technology                          |
|-----------|-------------------------------------|
| Frontend  | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript             |
| Backend   | Python (Flask)                      |
| Library   | [yt-dlp](https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp) |
| Hosting   | [Render](https://render.com)        |

